divs: Sighting DetailsIt was a cold winter night and I was bringing in some groceries from the car while I was inside my house putting down some of the groceries and my dad yelled out, "Come out here now!There's something weird out here!"So my mom and I went outside and saw three orblike things in a triangular shape and then while they were moving they changed to a singlefile line.The color of them were red-orange and yellow-orange.After about two or three minutes they started dissapering one by one. My mom took a picture of the triangular form check it out!
